column1: Instability troubled the early years of Kublai Khan's reign. Ogedei's grandson Kaidu refused to submit to Kublai and threatened the western frontier of Kublai's domain. The hostile but weakened Song dynasty remained an obstacle in the south. Kublai secured the northeast border in 1259 by installing the hostage prince Wonjong as the ruler of Korea, making it a Mongol tributary state. Kublai was also threatened by domestic unrest. Li Tan, the son-in-law of a powerful official, instigated a revolt against Mongol rule in 1262. After successfully suppressing the revolt, Kublai curbed the influence of the Han Chinese advisers in his court. He feared that his dependence on Chinese officials left him vulnerable to future revolts and defections to the Song.
column2: Nestabilnost je povzročila težave v zgodnjih letih vladanja Kublai Khana. Ogedejev vnuk Kaidu se ni hotel podrediti Kublaju in ogrožati zahodno mejo Kublajeve domene. Sovražna, a oslabljena dinastija Song je ostala ovira na jugu. Kublaj je leta 1259 zavaroval severovzhodno mejo z namestitvijo talca princa Wonjonga kot vladarja Koreje, zaradi česar je postala mongolska pritok. Kublaju so grozili tudi domači nemiri. Li Tan, zet močnega uradnika, je leta 1262 sprožil upor proti mongolski vladavini. Po uspešnem zatiranju upora je Kublai zajezil vpliv kitajskih svetovalcev Han na svojem dvoru. Bal se je, da bo zaradi odvisnosti od kitajskih uradnikov ranljiv za prihodnje upore in napake v pesmi.

column1: It is conjectured that a progressive decline in hormone levels with age is partially responsible for weakened immune responses in aging individuals. Conversely, some hormones are regulated by the immune system, notably thyroid hormone activity. The age-related decline in immune function is also related to decreasing vitamin D levels in the elderly. As people age, two things happen that negatively affect their vitamin D levels. First, they stay indoors more due to decreased activity levels. This means that they get less sun and therefore produce less cholecalciferol via UVB radiation. Second, as a person ages the skin becomes less adept at producing vitamin D.
column2: Domneva se, da je postopno zmanjšanje ravni hormonov s starostjo delno odgovoren za oslabljen imunski odziv pri staranju posameznikov. Nasprotno, nekateri hormoni so urejeni z imunskim sistemom, zlasti delovanje ščitničnega hormona. S starostjo povezano zmanjšanje imunske funkcije je povezano tudi z zniževanjem ravni vitamina D pri starejših. Ko se ljudje starajo, se zgodita dve stvari, ki negativno vplivata na njihovo raven vitamina D. Prvič, ostanejo bolj v zaprtih prostorih zaradi zmanjšane ravni aktivnosti. To pomeni, da dobijo manj sonca in zato proizvajajo manj holekalciferola preko UVB sevanja. Drugič, ko oseba stara, koža postane manj spretna pri proizvodnji vitamina D.

column1: The university operates 12 research institutes and 113 research centers on campus. Among these are the Oriental Institute—a museum and research center for Near Eastern studies owned and operated by the university—and a number of National Resource Centers, including the Center for Middle Eastern Studies. Chicago also operates or is affiliated with a number of research institutions apart from the university proper. The university partially manages Argonne National Laboratory, part of the United States Department of Energy's national laboratory system, and has a joint stake in Fermilab, a nearby particle physics laboratory, as well as a stake in the Apache Point Observatory in Sunspot, New Mexico. Faculty and students at the adjacent Toyota Technological Institute at Chicago collaborate with the university, In 2013, the university announced that it was affiliating the formerly independent Marine Biological Laboratory in Woods Hole, Mass. Although formally unrelated, the National Opinion Research Center is located on Chicago's campus.
column2: Univerza deluje 12 raziskovalni inštituti in 113 raziskovalni centri na kampusu. Med njimi so Orientalski inštitut – muzej in raziskovalni center za bližnjevzhodne študije v lasti in upravljanju univerze-in številnih nacionalnih centrov za vire, vključno s Centrom za bližnjevzhodne študije. Chicago prav tako deluje ali je povezana s številnimi raziskovalnimi ustanovami, razen univerze pravilno. Univerza delno upravlja Argonne National Laboratory, del nacionalnega laboratorijskega sistema ameriškega ministrstva za energijo in ima skupni delež v Fermilabu, bližnjem laboratoriju za fiziko delcev, kot tudi delež v observatoriju Apache Point v Sunspotu, Nova Mehika. Fakulteta in študenti na sosednjem Tehnološkem inštitutu Toyota v Chicagu sodelujejo z univerzo, Leta 2013, univerza je napovedala, da je bila povezana z nekdanjim neodvisnim morskim biološkim laboratorijem v Woods Hole, Mass. Čeprav formalno nepovezana, National Mnenje Raziskovalni center se nahaja na kampusu v Chicagu.

column1: The weight of boilers and condensers generally makes the power-to-weight ratio of a steam plant lower than for internal combustion engines. For mobile applications steam has been largely superseded by internal combustion engines or electric motors. However, most electric power is generated using steam turbine plant, so that indirectly the world's industry is still dependent on steam power. Recent concerns about fuel sources and pollution have incited a renewed interest in steam both as a component of cogeneration processes and as a prime mover. This is becoming known as the Advanced Steam movement.[citation needed]
column2: Zaradi teže kotlov in kondenzatorjev je razmerje med močjo in težo parne naprave na splošno nižje kot pri motorjih z notranjim zgorevanjem. Za mobilne aplikacije so paro v veliki meri nadomestili motorji z notranjim zgorevanjem ali elektromotorji. Vendar se večina električne energije proizvaja s parnimi turbinami, tako da je svetovna industrija posredno še vedno odvisna od pare. Nedavni pomisleki glede virov goriva in onesnaževanja so spodbudili ponovno zanimanje za paro kot sestavni del procesov soproizvodnje in kot glavni dejavnik. To postaja znano kot gibanje Napredno paro.

column1: Some elements of the Brotherhood, though perhaps against orders, did engage in violence against the government, and its founder Al-Banna was assassinated in 1949 in retaliation for the assassination of Egypt's premier Mahmud Fami Naqrashi three months earlier. The Brotherhood has suffered periodic repression in Egypt and has been banned several times, in 1948 and several years later following confrontations with Egyptian president Gamal Abdul Nasser, who jailed thousands of members for several years.

Bratovščina je doživela periodično represijo v Egiptu in je bila večkrat prepovedana, leta 1948 in nekaj let kasneje po spopadih z egiptovskim predsednikom Gamalom Abdulom Nasserjem, ki je več let zaprl na tisoče članov.

column1: Kublai Khan promoted commercial, scientific, and cultural growth. He supported the merchants of the Silk Road trade network by protecting the Mongol postal system, constructing infrastructure, providing loans that financed trade caravans, and encouraging the circulation of paper banknotes (鈔, Chao). Pax Mongolica, Mongol peace, enabled the spread of technologies, commodities, and culture between China and the West. Kublai expanded the Grand Canal from southern China to Daidu in the north. Mongol rule was cosmopolitan under Kublai Khan. He welcomed foreign visitors to his court, such as the Venetian merchant Marco Polo, who wrote the most influential European account of Yuan China. Marco Polo's travels would later inspire many others like Christopher Columbus to chart a passage to the Far East in search of its legendary wealth.
column2: Kublai Khan je spodbujal gospodarsko, znanstveno in kulturno rast. Trgovce trgovske mreže Silk Road je podpiral z zaščito mongolskega poštnega sistema, gradnjo infrastrukture, zagotavljanjem posojil, s katerimi so se financirale trgovske prikolice, in spodbujanjem obtoka papirnatih bankovcev (±, Chao). Pax Mongolica, mongolski mir, je omogočil širjenje tehnologij, dobrin in kulture med Kitajsko in Zahodom. Kublai je razširil Grand Canal iz južne Kitajske na Daidu na severu. Mongolska vladavina je bila svetovljanka pod Kublai Kanom. Na svojem dvoru je sprejel tuje obiskovalce, kot je beneški trgovec Marco Polo, ki je napisal najvplivnejši evropski račun Yuana Kitajske. Potovanja Marca Pola so kasneje navdihnila mnoge druge, kot je Krištof Kolumb, da bi začrtali prehod na Daljni vzhod v iskanju legendarnega bogastva.

column1: Demographically, it was the most diverse city in Poland, with significant numbers of foreign-born inhabitants. In addition to the Polish majority, there was a significant Jewish minority in Warsaw. According to Russian census of 1897, out of the total population of 638,000, Jews constituted 219,000 (around 34% percent). Warsaw's prewar Jewish population of more than 350,000 constituted about 30 percent of the city's total population. In 1933, out of 1,178,914 inhabitants 833,500 were of Polish mother tongue. World War II changed the demographics of the city, and to this day there is much less ethnic diversity than in the previous 300 years of Warsaw's history. Most of the modern day population growth is based on internal migration and urbanisation.
column2: Demografsko je bilo to najbolj raznoliko mesto na Poljskem z velikim številom prebivalcev, rojenih v tujini. Poleg poljske večine je bila v Varšavi pomembna judovska manjšina. Po ruskem popisu iz leta 1897 je od celotnega prebivalstva 638.000 Judov predstavljalo 219.000 Judov (približno 34 % odstotkov). Predvojna judovska populacija v Varšavi, ki je obsegala več kot 350.000 prebivalcev, je predstavljala približno 30 odstotkov celotnega mestnega prebivalstva. Leta 1933 je bilo od 1.178.914 prebivalcev 833.500 prebivalcev poljskega maternega jezika. Druga svetovna vojna je spremenila demografijo mesta in do danes je etnična raznolikost veliko manjša kot v prejšnjih 300 letih Varšave. Večina sodobne rasti prebivalstva temelji na notranjih migracijah in urbanizaciji.

column1: During this time, the discovery of oil in the North Sea and the following "It's Scotland's oil" campaign of the Scottish National Party (SNP) resulted in rising support for Scottish independence, as well as the SNP. The party argued that the revenues from the oil were not benefitting Scotland as much as they should. The combined effect of these events led to Prime Minister Wilson committing his government to some form of devolved legislature in 1974. However, it was not until 1978 that final legislative proposals for a Scottish Assembly were passed by the United Kingdom Parliament.
column2: V tem času je odkritje nafte v Severnem morju in naslednja nafta Škotske narodne stranke (SNP) povzročila večjo podporo škotski neodvisnosti in SNP. Stran je trdila, da prihodki od nafte Škotski niso koristili toliko, kot bi morali. Skupni učinek teh dogodkov je privedel do tega, da je predsednik vlade Wilson leta 1974 svojo vlado zavezal neki obliki decentraliziranega zakonodajnega obdobja. Vendar je parlament Združenega kraljestva sprejel končne zakonodajne predloge za škotsko skupščino šele leta 1978.

column1: In the 1970s, the city was the subject of a song, "Walking Into Fresno", written by Hall Of Fame guitarist Bill Aken and recorded by Bob Gallion of the world-famous "WWVA Jamboree" radio and television show in Wheeling, West Virginia. Aken, adopted by Mexican movie actress Lupe Mayorga, grew up in the neighboring town of Madera and his song chronicled the hardships faced by the migrant farm workers he saw as a child. Aken also made his first TV appearance playing guitar on the old country-western show at The Fresno Barn.
column2: V sedemdesetih letih prejšnjega stoletja je bilo mesto predmet pesmi„Walking Into Fresno“, ki jo je napisal kitarist Hall Of Fame Bill Aken, posnel pa jo je Bob Gallion s svetovno znanega radia in televizijske oddaje„WWVA Jamboree“v Wheelingu v Zahodni Virginiji. Aken, ki ga je posvojila mehiška filmska igralka Lupe Mayorga, je odraščal v sosednjem mestu Madera in njegova pesem je kronizirala stiske, s katerimi se soočajo delavci migrantske kmetije, ki jih je videl kot otrok. Aken je tudi svoj prvi televizijski nastop igral kitaro na stari country-zahodni oddaji v Fresno barnu.
